va:valueAssertion.test: iaf:numeric-greater-equal-than(iaf:sum((iaf:sum($a), $b, iaf:numeric-unary-minus(iaf:sum($i)))), iaf:sum((iaf:sum($c), iaf:sum($d), iaf:sum($e), iaf:sum($f), iaf:sum($g), iaf:sum($h))))

pf:period.test: if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate else false()
if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate else false()
if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate else false()

if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate + xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') - xs:yearMonthDuration('P1M') - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') else false()

if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate + xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') - xs:yearMonthDuration('P2M') - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') else false()

if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate + xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') - xs:yearMonthDuration('P3M') - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') else false()

if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate + xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') - xs:yearMonthDuration('P4M') - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') else false()

if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate + xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') - xs:yearMonthDuration('P5M') - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D') else false()
if (xfi:is-instant-period(.)) then xs:date(xfi:period-instant(.) - xs:dayTimeDuration('P1D')) = $refPeriodEndDate else false()
